name: プロデューサー
text: なんだなんだ、\n当然みたいな顔して！
trans:
What's this, what's this, huh?
Acting like it was settled from the start!

name: 透
text: 勝つって言ったでしょ
trans: I said I was going to win, right?

name: プロデューサー
text: ──うん、よく頑張った\n頑張ってくれたことも勝ってくれたことも、嬉しいよ
trans:
──Yeah, you did good.
Makes me happy you could give it your all, that you could clinch victory.

name: 透
text: うん、でもまだ……\n途中だからね
trans:
Yeah. But, still...
We're only halfway after all, right?
